Technology Stack Used
Frontend:
HTML5: For structuring the web pages.
CSS3: For styling and layout.
JavaScript: For interactive elements.
React.js: For building the user interface.
Backend:
Node.js: For server-side scripting.
Express.js: For building the web application framework.
MongoDB: For the database to store movie data and user preferences.
Python: For implementing recommendation algorithms (if applicable).
Libraries & Frameworks:
TensorFlow: For implementing machine learning algorithms (if applicable).
scikit-learn: For data analysis and machine learning (if applicable).
Axios: For making HTTP requests to the backend.
Tools:
Git: Version control.
Postman: For testing APIs.
VS Code: Code editor.
